# Team Task Manager

A full-stack project management application with role-based access control.

## Tech Stack
- React + Vite + Tailwind
- Node.js + Express
- PostgreSQL + Prisma
- JWT Authentication

## Features
- Admin & Member roles
- Project & Task management
- Google OAuth login
- Dashboard analytics

## Setup

### Backend
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev

### Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev